mozilla-rootcerts

Keyboard layout checkpoint:
/etc/wscons.conf
 #encoding sv
 #encoding us.swapctrlcaps
 encoding jp

/root/.xinitrc
 setxkbmap -model jp106 jp

Build sample script:
 https://github.com/ebijun/NetBSD/tree/master/zaurus/Image

